Name: ATAX
Version: 3.9
Summary: Package for doing Einnahmen-Ausgabenrechnung according to Austrian tax laws.
Home-page: https://codeberg.org/tanzer/tapyr
Author: Christian Tanzer
Author-email: tanzer@swing.co.at
